Hypo Real Estate’s bonds previously seemed to be an alternative speculation placement, now their value must be regarded as dependent on the stability of the international banking system after the net aggravation of the banking crisis and the crisis of the institution itself that made the crisis enter the establishment by the purchase of the Depfa bank.
As long as emission institutions, governments, and commercial banks are still ready to support the system, we can assume a resorption of the remnants over time.
Or it will happen what no one dare to expect at this time – that the financial crisis can be overcome in the next 15 months.
